---
---
<section id="security" class="privacy-section" style="scroll-margin-top:6rem;">
  <div class="privacy-inner">
    <p class="privacy-label">Security</p>
    <h2 class="privacy-heading">Your Privacy, Our Priority.</h2>
    <p class="privacy-subtitle">We protect your data as if it were our own, following the most rigorous industry standards.</p>
    <div class="privacy-grid">
      <div class="privacy-card">
        <p class="privacy-card-title">SOC 2-Aligned Framework</p>
        <p class="privacy-card-body">Our systems are architected based on SOC 2 principles, ensuring strict access controls and data integrity from day one.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="privacy-card">
        <p class="privacy-card-title">World-Class Infrastructure</p>
        <p class="privacy-card-body">We leverage industry-leading cloud providers (like AWS) to ensure your records are stored in highly secure, bank-grade encrypted environments.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="privacy-card">
        <p class="privacy-card-title">Zero-Training Pledge</p>
        <p class="privacy-card-body">We use private AI instances. Your conversations are never used to train our models or shared with third parties for their AI improvement.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="privacy-card">
        <p class="privacy-card-title">End-to-End Encryption</p>
        <p class="privacy-card-body">Every recording is encrypted at rest and in transit. You hold the key to your client's trust.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style is:global>
/* -- Privacy Section -- */
.privacy-section { background: #f7fbff; padding: 4rem 1.25rem; }
@media (min-width: 640px) { .privacy-section { padding: 6rem 2rem; } }
.privacy-inner { max-width: 1160px; margin: 0 auto; }
.privacy-label {
  font-size: 0.78rem; font-weight: 800; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.12em; color: #1f8fff; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
}
.privacy-heading {
  max-width: 40rem; margin: 0 auto 1rem; text-align: center;
  font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: -0.02em; color: #07111f; line-height: 1.1;
}
@media (min-width: 640px) { .privacy-heading { font-size: 2.85rem; } }
.privacy-subtitle {
  max-width: 36rem; margin: 0 auto 3rem; text-align: center;
  font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.6; color: #53647a;
}
.privacy-grid {
  display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 1.5rem;
}
@media (min-width: 768px) { .privacy-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; } }
.privacy-card {
  border-radius: 1rem; border: 1px solid #dce7f1; background: #fff; padding: 1.5rem;
  box-shadow: 0 20px 34px -24px rgba(9,21,42,0.36);
}
.privacy-card-title { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 800; color: #07111f; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
.privacy-card-body { font-size: 0.88rem; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.65; color: #53647a; }
</style>
